title: Task Forces Complete List - Images
content:
[[iftags +fragment]]

This fragment page, due to the character limit of a single page, hosts the images from [[[task-forces-complete-list| A Comprehensive List of Mobile Task Forces]]]. 

To ensure correct attribution of all logos, please add the licensing information for any insignia you add to the licenseboxhosted on [[[fragment:task-forces-complete-list-licensebox|this fragment page]]].

[[/iftags]]
